      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dice the<strong> mozzarella </strong>into small bite-sized pieces and add to some kitchen paper</p><p>Press down on the <strong>diced mozzarella</strong> with another piece of kitchen paper to squeeze out as much liquid as you can</p>",
