      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>into rings</p><p>Deseed the <strong>green pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
